</p>

<strong>Opting-Out</strong>
<p>We respect your privacy and ability to choose whether to share information with us. If you receive communications from us that you prefer not to receive, you may opt out from receiving these communications, by modifying the contact options in your preferences profile.</p>

<strong>Contacting Us</strong>
<p>
If you have any questions or comments about our Privacy Policy, please e-mail us at info@feedbacksafe.com.
</p>

